               <msContents>
                  <summary>Admonitions of Monastic Fathers for Monks: Sayings of Abba Bawmin and other monastic leaders; Monastic Orders of Pachomius, ሥርዓተ፡ ጳኵሚስ፡.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="36v" facs="003">Fols 1r–36v</locus>
                     <title>Sayings of Abba Bawmin and other monastic leaders</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎ይቤ፡ ባውሚን፡ ንብረቱ፡ ለመነኮስ፡ ሥሙር፡ ውእቱ፡ በግብረ፡ ‎‎እደዊከ፡ ተሴሰይ፡ ወመካንከ፡ አጽንዕ፡ ኢትበል፡ ለፌ፡ ወለፌ። ‎‎መነኮስ፡ ዘይፈልስ፡ እመካኑ፡ ይመስል፡ ከመ፡ ዕፅ፡ ዘመልሕዎ፡ ‎‎ወይተክልዎ፡ በበምንት።‎<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="36v" to="60r" facs="039">Fols 36v–60r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2228Ruleso">Rules of
                                                  Pachomius</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎ነገር፡ ዘአባ፡ ጳኩሚስ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ዘተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ለእለ፡ ‎‎ይገብሩ፡ ፈቃደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ትምህርተ፡ አበው፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ‎‎ኵሉ፡ እመን፡ በ፩ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ፈጣሬ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ ‎‎ውእቱ፡‎<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
