                          <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="003">Fol. iir(ecto)</locus>
                          <desc>Calendar, Instructions about the measurement of shadows for the ‎telling of time for the whole year, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥፍረ፡ ሰዓታት፡</foreign></desc>
                        </item>
